{"thig3.1:0.1":"Therigatha 3.1 ","thig3.1:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thig3.1:0.3":"Aparasamatherigatha ","thig3.1:1.1":"“Pannavisativassani, ","thig3.1:1.2":"yato pabbajitaya me; ","thig3.1:1.3":"Nabhijanami cittassa, ","thig3.1:1.4":"samam laddham kudacanam. ","thig3.1:2.1":"Aladdha cetaso santim, ","thig3.1:2.2":"citte avasavattini; ","thig3.1:2.3":"Tato samvegamapadim, ","thig3.1:2.4":"saritva jinasasanam. ","thig3.1:3.1":"Bahuhi dukkhadhammehi, ","thig3.1:3.2":"appamadarataya me; ","thig3.1:3.3":"Tanhakkhayo anuppatto, ","thig3.1:3.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thig3.1:3.5":"Ajja me sattami ratti, ","thig3.1:3.6":"yato tanha visosita”ti. ","thig3.1:4.1":"… Apara sama theri …. "}